  ## How do I designate my avatar?

  An avatar is a picture or photo you choose to represent you.  It can be an actual photo of yourself or, more likely, an alternate image, one used to protect your privacy.  Your avatar and username are the cornerstone of your digital, online representation.

  <figure>
